who done right by me?

166
00:07:30,200 --> 00:07:31,236
That ain't in the Bible.

167
00:07:31,320 --> 00:07:32,595
We ain't talking about
what's in the Bible.

168
00:07:32,720 --> 00:07:34,871
What sense it make to shop there
when she overcharges?

169
