00:30:28,760 --> 00:30:30,433
Seems like something ought to be done
to help him.

708
00:30:30,520 --> 00:30:31,840
The man don't bother nobody.

709
00:30:31,920 --> 00:30:34,276
He just mixed up
'cause of that metal plate

710
00:30:34,360 --> 00:30:37,034
he got in his head. Ain't no sense in...

711
