712
00:30:40,240 --> 00:30:41,560
At least he'd be eating right.

713
00:30:41,640 --> 00:30:43,040
They could help him take care of himself.

714
00:30:43,120 --> 00:30:44,713
Don't nobody want to be locked up, Rose.

715
00:30:44,800 --> 00:30:46,678
What you want to lock the man up for?

716
00:30:46,760 --> 00:30:48,399
Man going down there,

717
00:30:48,480 --> 00:30:52,679
over there and fight that war,
messing with them Japs,

718
00:30:52,760 --> 00:30:54,433
getting half his head blown off.

719
00:30:54,520 --> 00:30:58,230
They give him a lousy $3,000.
I got to swoop down on that.

720
00:30:58,320 --> 00:30:59,640
Is you fixing to get into that again?

721
00:30:59,720 --> 00:31:01,757
He got a metal plate in his head.

722
00:31:01,880 --> 00:31:03,917
That's the only reason
I got a roof over my head

723
00:31:04,000 --> 00:31:05,514
is 'cause of that metal plate.

724
00:31:05,600 --> 00:31:07,432
Ain't no sense in you
blaming yourself for nothing.

725
00:31:07,520 --> 00:31:09,716
Gabe was in no condition
to manage that money.

726
00:31:09,800 --> 00:31:10,916
You done what was right by him.

727
00:31:11,000 --> 00:31:13,037
Can't nobody say
you ain't done what was right by him.

728
00:31:13,120 --> 00:31:14,474
Look how long you took care of him.

729
00:31:14,600 --> 00:31:17,195
Till he wanted his own place
and moved over there with Miss Pearl.

730
00:31:17,280 --> 00:31:19,795
That ain't what I'm saying, woman.
I'm just...

731
00:31:22,400 --> 00:31:23,834
I'm just stating the facts.

732
00:31:23,920 --> 00:31:25,991
If my brother
didn't have a metal plate in his head,

733
00:31:26,080 --> 00:31:27,514
