staring right back at me.

2308
02:04:05,600 --> 02:04:08,752
Hiding under the bed, in the closet.

2309
02:04:08,840 --> 02:04:11,878
I'm just saying I got to find a way
to get rid of that shadow, Mama.

2310
02:04:11,960 --> 02:04:14,191
You just like him.
You got him in you good.

2311
02:04:14,280 --> 02:04:15,430
