2312
02:04:15,520 --> 02:04:19,196
- You Troy Maxson all over again.
- I don't want to be Troy Maxson!

2313
02:04:20,520 --> 02:04:22,113
I just want to be me.

2314
02:04:22,200 --> 02:04:25,113
You can't be nobody but who you are, Cory.

2315
02:04:25,200 --> 02:04:28,272
That shadow wasn't nothing
but you growing into yourself.

2316
02:04:28,480 --> 02:04:30,437
