I thought when I seen him.

2331
02:05:21,680 --> 02:05:23,990
I thought, "Rose Lee,

2332
02:05:24,680 --> 02:05:26,797
"here's a man you can open yourself up to

2333
02:05:26,880 --> 02:05:29,076
