"you been tipping around the edges of."

2336
02:05:43,360 --> 02:05:46,353
When your daddy walked through the house,

2337
02:05:46,440 --> 02:05:48,113
he was just

2338
02:05:49,280 --> 02:05:51,636
so big.

2339
02:05:53,360 --> 02:05:55,033
